<!-- ============================================================
     FAQ
     ============================================================ -->
<section class="section section--alt faq" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
      <h2>Common questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Is the 24-hour deadline guaranteed?
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          <p>For standard landing pages, yes. The clock starts once you approve the brief and share your content. More complex projects have a fixed deadline agreed upfront — you always know your delivery date before we start.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Will my page look like a template?
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          <p>No. Every page we build is designed specifically for your business and goal — not pulled from a library and filled in. That's why our pages load faster, convert better and look different from everything else in your market.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          Do I need to have a domain or hosting already?
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          <p>No. Hosting is free and included in every project. If you have a domain, we connect it. If you don't, we help you get one. Your page goes live with a secure certificate automatically — nothing for you to set up.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          What happens after delivery? Can I make changes?
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          <p>Every project includes revision rounds before we launch. After delivery, our $50/month maintenance plan covers text updates, image swaps and small layout changes whenever you need them. Larger changes are quoted separately.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          How does payment work?
          <span class="faq-icon" aria-hidden="true">+</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer" hidden>
          <p>50% upfront when we start, 50% when you approve the final result. We accept credit card, bank transfer and PayPal. You never pay the second half until you've seen and approved the finished page.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============================================================
     CONTACT
